milestones.description: Dennis Lillee has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs for AUS, going past Allan Border's 2
Geoff Dymock and Kim Hughes's 33-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 22 between Dennis Lillee and Jeff Hammond
Geoff Boycott has become the top scorer for ENG in ODIs with 891 runs, going past Dennis Amiss's 859
Ian Botham has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (30) for ENG, going past Chris Old
